<!-- ═══ NARRATIVE ═══ -->
<section class="sp-narrative">
  <div class="sp-narrative-inner">
    <h2 class="sp-narrative-heading reveal">THE WORK</h2>

    <div class="reveal">
      <p>GoCompliance is an enterprise compliance platform by GoSaaS, built in partnership with Oracle. The existing product worked but the interface was dense, unintuitive, and had accumulated years of feature additions without a cohesive design pass.</p>

      <p>I improved the core UX/UI — simplifying navigation, restructuring information hierarchy, and bringing visual consistency to a platform that enterprise compliance officers use daily. The goal was to make a complex regulatory tool feel manageable without dumbing it down.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

